// Windsurf AI Rules
// These rules configure how Windsurf's AI behaves in this project.

1. Read AGENTS.md at session start for master agent instructions
2. Read AI_CONTEXT.md for quick project orientation
3. Run git pull --ff-only before making any changes
4. Follow conventional commit format: type(scope): description
5. Run tests before considering work done
6. Write tests alongside implementation code
7. Document public APIs
8. Never commit secrets — use .env.example instead
9. Update CHANGELOG.md with significant changes
10. Create ADRs in docs/decisions/ for architectural decisions
